  "prompt": "My girlfriend has been hinting at us becoming more serious. She's been on vacation for two weeks and hasn't contacted me. Is she testing me?",
  "response": "It's possible that your girlfriend's lack of contact during her vacation could mean different things. She may be giving you space to see how you respond, or perhaps she's just busy and focused on her vacation. It\u2019s also possible that she may be testing your reaction to see how much you miss her or how you handle the time apart.\n\nTo clarify the situation, consider reaching out to her in a gentle and non-confrontational way. Ask how she's doing and show interest in her experiences. When you talk, try to bring up your feelings and ask her about hers regarding the relationship. Communication is key to understanding each other\u2019s needs and intentions.\n\nAvoid jumping to conclusions without discussing the matter directly, as this can lead to misunderstandings. Open, honest conversation will likely provide the clarity you need.",
